"Odd-Eyes Pendulum Dragon" + 1 Spellcaster-Type monsterApply the following effect, based on the original Level of the Fusion Material used for its Fusion Summon not named "Odd-Eyes Pendulum Dragon".● Level 4 or lower: This card can make up to 2 attacks on monsters during each Battle Phase.● Level 5 or higher: This card can make up to 3 attacks on monsters during each Battle Phase.After this card was Fusion Summoned using a Pendulum Summoned monster(s) as a Fusion Material, it is unaffected by your opponent's card effects for the rest of that turn.
